	"_data": {
		"_scalar": {
			"_restrict": ["_mod"],
			...
		}
	}
}
```

The above example describes a [scalar](_scalar.md) variable whose *value*, once set, *cannot* be *modified*. It is, however, *possible* to [add](_add.md) or, or [delete](_del.md) the *property*.

